<h1 class="align-center">ISA Monthly Billing Statement</h1>
<hr width="370" style="border: solid 1px #dbdbdb;" />

<p>Hai <strong>\{{student.name}}</strong>,</p>

<p>Tagihan Income Sharing Agreement (ISA) Anda untuk program Fullstack Javascript Hacktiv8 telah tersedia.</p>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
  <tr>
  <td><strong>Billing Code</strong></td>
    <td>: \{{billing_statement.code}}</td>
    <td><strong>Phone Number</strong></td>
    <td>: \{{student.phone}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Contract ID</strong></td>
    <td>: \{{agreement_contract.id}}</td>
    <td><strong>Student Email</strong></td>
    <td>: \{{student.email}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Print Date</strong></td>
    <td>: \{{billing_statement.print_date}}</td>
    <td></td>
    <td></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br />
<br />
<h2>Transaction Summary</h2>
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
  <tr class="table-header">
    <td><strong>Total Billing Amount</strong></td>
    <td><strong>Min Payment</strong></td>
    <td><strong>Payment Due Date</strong></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="table-body">\{{billing_statement.total_amount}}</td>
    <td class="table-body">\{{billing_statement.min_payment}}</td>
    <td class="table-body">\{{billing_statement.due_date}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br />
<br />
<h2>Transaction Details</h2>
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
  <tr class="table-header">
    <td><strong>Transaction Date</strong></td>
    <td><strong>Posting Date</strong></td>
    <td><strong>Transaction Description</strong></td>
    <td><strong>Amount</strong></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    \{{#each billing_transactions}}
      <td class="table-body"\>\{{transaction_date}}</td>
      <td class="table-body"\>\{{posting_date}}</td>
      <td class="table-body"\>\{{description}}</td>
      <td class="table-body"\>\{{amount}}</td>
    \{{\each}}
  </tr>
  <tr class="table-footer">
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td>Total</td>
      <td>\{{billing_statement.total_amount}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<br />
<br />
<p>Pembayaran dapat dilakukan dengan cara transfer ke salah satu virtual account Bank di
bawah ini :</p>

<br />
<br />
<h2>Payment Method</h2>
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
  <tr class="table-header">
    <td>
      Virtual Account Name
    </td>
    <td>
      Virtual Account Number
    </td>
  </tr>
  \{{#each contract_vas}}
    <td class="table-body">\{{ bank_name }}</td>
    <td class="table-body">\{{ va_number }}</td>
  \{{/each}}
</table>

<p>
Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan, silakan hubungi kami melalui email: <strong>kontakisa@hacktiv8.com</strong>, atau telepon: <strong>(021) 1234567890</strong> yang aktif selama jam operasional, <strong>Senin-Jumat pukul 08.30 - 17.00 WIB</strong>.
</p>
